Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Used to add to an entity's list of targets.

Usage
-----

*float* appendTarget( *entity* **target** )

Parameters
----------

-   [target] - Entity to be targetted.

